{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"94d454db42","title":"陈云在中央工作会议上的书面发言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c1467b7e3","index":0,"year":1977,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"94d454db42","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"陈云","id":"a2f6c6af57","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"异端思潮","id":"ca0e96a612","type":"主题"},{"name":"对文革的评价和政策","id":"d8ee3d1fe9","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"747eac0a0d","name":"陈云"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"84deff9d94","type":"title","text":"陈云在中央工作会议上的书面发言","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ada918ae6b","type":"paragraph","text":"摘要：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"efff27f128","type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎“四人帮”反革命集团，这是我们党的一个伟大胜利，对中国革命具有伟大的历史意义。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b2debadc1","type":"paragraph","text":"我对天安门事件的看法：","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1fa6c195f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）当时绝大多数群众是为了悼念周总理。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f67aca4e23","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）尤其关心周恩来同志逝世后党的接班人是谁。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8abab2939","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）至于混在群众中的坏人是极少数。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d058acd10c","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）需要查一查“四人帮”是否插手，是否有诡计。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6041e3871","type":"paragraph","text":"因为天安门事件是群众关心的事，而且当时在全国也有类似事件。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72023d5efd","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平同志与天安门事件是无关的。为了中国革命和中国共产党的需要，听说中央有些同志提出让邓小平同志重新参加党中央的领导工作，是完全正确、完全必要的，我完全拥护。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"94d454db42","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}